quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  38,52,"And at them (are) the eyes`/eye lids` confining/limiting/restricting, same age/not aging"
  38,53,That (is) what you are being promised to the Account Day/Resurrection Day
  38,54,"That (E) this (is) Our provision (E), (there is) nothing from (a) depletion from it"
  38,55,"This, and that truly to the tyrannizing/arrogant (is a) bad/evil (E) return"
  38,56,"Hell they roast/suffer (from) it, so how bad (are) the beds (destination)"
  38,57,"This, so they will taste/experience it hot/cold water , and cold/decayed/rotten"
  38,58,And other/another from its likeness/similarity spouses
  38,59,"This (is a) group/crowd bursting/plunging with you, (there is) no welcome with (for) them, that they are, they are entering/suffering the fire"
  38,60,"They said: \"But you are (there is) no welcome with (for) you, you advanced/introduced it for us.\" So how bad (is) the settlement/decision"
  38,61,"They said: \"Our Lord who advanced/introduced this for us, so increase him (with) a double torture in the fire"
  38,62,"And they said: \"Why (is it) for us, we do not see men, we were, we count them from the bad/evil/harmful"
  38,63,We took them (by) mocking/ridiculing or the eyesights/knowledge deviated/turned away from them
  38,64,"That truly that (is) true/fact (E) , the fire`s people dispute/ controvert/argue (among them selves)"
  38,65,"Say: \"Truly I am (a) warner/giver of notice, and (there is) none from a God, except God the one, the defeator/conqueror"
  38,66,"The skies`/space`s and the earth`s/Planet Earth`s Lord, and what (is) between them (B), the glorious/mighty ,the forgiving often/forgiver"
  38,67,"Say: \"Is it (a) great news/information"
  38,68,You are from it objecting/opposing
  38,69,"(There) was not from knowledge to me with the group/assembly/nobles, the highest/mightiest when they dispute/controvert/argue"
  38,70,That (it) is (only) inspired/transmitted to me except that I am a clear/evident warner/giver of notice
  38,71,"When your Lord said to the angels: \"That I am creating a human from mud/clay"
  38,72,"So if I straightened him, and I blew in him from My Soul/Spirit , so fall/come to him prostrating"
  38,73,"So the angels prostrated all of them, all/all together"
  38,74,"Except Satan he became arrogant, and was/is from the disbelievers"
  38,75,"He said: \"You Satan , what prevented/prohibited you that you prostrate to what I created with My hands, did you become arrogant, or you were from the high and mighty"
  38,76,"He said: \"I am better than him, You created me from fire and You created him from mud/clay"
  38,77,"He said: \"So get out/emerge from it, so that you are cursed/expelled"
  38,78,And that (E) on you (is) My curse/torture/expulsion to the Judgment Day/Resurrection Day
  38,79,"He said: \"My Lord so give me time/delay me to a day/time they be sent/resurrected/revived"
  38,80,"He said: \"So that you are from the given time/delayed"
  38,81,"To day/time (of) the time, the known"
  38,82,"He said: \"So with Your glory/might , I will misguide/lure them (E) all/all together"
  38,83,"Except Your worshippers/slaves from them, the faithful/devoted"
  38,84,"He said: So the truth and the truth I say"
  38,85,I will fill (E) Hell from you and from who followed you from them all/all together
  38,86,"Say: \"I do not ask/question you on it from a reward/wage/fee, and I am not from the pretentious/meddling"
  38,87,That (E) it is except a reminder/remembrance to the creations all together/(universes)
  38,88,And you will know (E) its news/information after a time/period of time
  39,1,"The Book`s descent from God, the glorious/mighty , the wise/judicious"
  39,2,"That We, We descended to you The Book with the truth so worship God faithful, loyal/devoted to him (in) the religion"
  39,3,"Is not to God the religion the clear/pure? And those who took from other than Him guardians/allies (they say): We do not worship them except to near/approach us to God, (an) approachment/ degree .\" That truly God judges/rules between them in what they are in it differing/disputing , that truly God does not guide who he is lying/denying/falsifying , (an insistent) disbeliever"
  39,4,"If God wanted/intended that (E) He takes a child (son), He would have chosen/purified from who He created, what He wills/wants, His praise/glory, He is God, the one the defeator/conqueror (E)"
  39,5,"He created the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth, with the truth . He rotates/rolls the night on (to) the daytime, and He rotates/rolls the daytime on (to) the night, and He manipulated/subjugated the sun and the moon, each/all flows/orbits to a term/time, named/identified (specified), is He not the glorious/mighty , the forgiving/often forgiver"
  39,6,"He created you from one self , then He made/created from it, its spouse , and He descended for you from the camels/livestock eight pairs/kinds (refer to 6:143 and 6:144), He creates you, in your mothers` bellies/insides, a creation from after a creation, in 3 darknesses (trimesters), that one, (is) God, your Lord, for Him (is) the kingdom/ownership (there is) no god except Him, so how/where (do) you be diverted/misguided"
  39,7,"If you disbelieve, so then God (is) rich from (without) you, and He does not accept/approve the disbelief to His worshippers/slaves , and if you thank/be grateful He accepts/approves it for you, and no sinner/loader/burdener carries/bears another`s sins/load/burden , then to your Lord (is) your return, so He informs you with what you were making/doing , that He truly (is) knowledgeable with of the chests (innermosts)"